need an art gallery.

00:06:24.260 --> 00:06:27.376 align:middle line:90%
What we need is a coffee shop.

00:06:27.376 --> 00:06:29.500 align:middle line:84%
>> Actually, that's what
I wanted in New York City.

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:34.400 align:middle line:10%
I was enamoured of the idea of
the bohemian New York coffee

00:06:34.400 --> 00:06:38.280 align:middle line:10%
shop scene, and
poetry, and jazz.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:39.950 align:middle line:90%
And I couldn't find it anywhere.

00:06:39.950 --> 00:06:43.340 align:middle line:84%
And that's what
happened at Life Cafe.

00:06:43.340 --> 00:06:45.920 align:middle line:84%
All I really did was give
it a place to happen.

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:49.380 align:middle line:84%
But it filled up with
jazz, and poetry, and art,

00:06:49.380 --> 00:06:52.940 align:middle line:84%
and a wonderful
community of friends.

00:06:52.940 --> 00:06:57.087 align:middle line:84%
>> I got a job working at Life
Cafe as a waitress in 1985.

00:06:57.087 --> 00:06:58.170 align:middle line:90%
And so I was 18 years old.

00:06:58.170 --> 00:07:00.260 align:middle line:84%
And that's when I
met David and Sharon.

00:07:00.260 --> 00:07:01.760 align:middle line:84%
He was in his 30's
when I met him.

00:07:01.760 --> 00:07:05.390 align:middle line:84%
But to me, he just seemed like
this responsible older man.

00:07:05.390 --> 00:07:07.430 align:middle line:84%
In many ways, he was an
incredible businessman

00:07:07.430 --> 00:07:08.230 align:middle line:90%
and visionary.

00:07:08.230 --> 00:07:09.890 align:middle line:84%
And in other ways,
he was horrible

00:07:09.890 --> 00:07:13.580 align:middle line:84%
because there was no one
who came into that cafe

00:07:13.580 --> 00:07:15.560 align:middle line:84%
who, if they needed
a free cup of coffee

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.630 align:middle line:84%
or a free meal that day,
that wouldn't give it

00:07:17.630 --> 00:07:19.520 align:middle line:84%
to them without any
question or hesitation.

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:20.700 align:middle line:90%
>> It was a lot of fun.

00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:22.741 align:middle line:84%
It was a lot of fun
waitressing at the Life Cafe.

00:07:22.741 --> 00:07:26.870 align:middle line:84%
There were all these Vietnam
vets that would hang out there.

00:07:26.870 --> 00:07:28.630 align:middle line:90%
They'd be smoking pot.

00:07:28.630 --> 00:07:30.710 align:middle line:84%
You know, come on,
sweetie, give me a refill.

00:07:30.710 --> 00:07:33.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Life Cafe was a
really important element

00:07:33.290 --> 00:07:34.370 align:middle line:90%
in the neighborhood.

00:07:34.370 --> 00:07:37.550 align:middle line:84%
The people that own art
galleries would meet in there,

00:07:37.550 --> 00:07:40.910 align:middle line:84%
and musicians would drop
by and just start playing.

00:07:40.910 --> 00:07:42.620 align:middle line:90%
It was a focal point.

00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:44.750 align:middle line:84%
>> There was one
area in the cafe,

00:07:44.750 --> 00:07:46.880 align:middle line:84%
if you got that
particular section,

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:50.480 align:middle line:84%
