afford to pay for anything.

00:07:53.629 --> 00:07:55.670 align:middle line:84%
They were certainly not
going to leave you a tip.

00:07:55.670 --> 00:07:57.770 align:middle line:84%
And they were camping
out there all day

00:07:57.770 --> 00:08:01.100 align:middle line:84%
long, playing checkers,
chess, cards, whatever.

00:08:01.100 --> 00:08:03.751 align:middle line:84%
And David would never
tell them to leave.

00:08:03.751 --> 00:08:07.188 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:07.188 --> 00:08:14.553 align:middle line:90%


00:08:14.553 --> 00:08:19.490 align:middle line:84%
>> Sound is god, is
god, is god, is god.

00:08:19.490 --> 00:08:25.130 align:middle line:10%
>> I formed a band with a very
talented woman, Sue Ann Harkey,

00:08:25.130 --> 00:08:26.240 align:middle line:10%
