New York in 1983.

00:08:42.110 --> 00:08:43.684 align:middle line:90%
And that's how I met David.

00:08:43.684 --> 00:08:47.840 align:middle line:90%


00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:49.760 align:middle line:84%
>> It was loud and
it was screechy.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:52.280 align:middle line:84%
And it was all these
weird instruments.

00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:55.850 align:middle line:90%
