00:09:09.390 --> 00:09:11.360 align:middle line:90%
>> Very, very long, black hair.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:14.120 align:middle line:90%
And she had a green streak.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:16.790 align:middle line:90%
And she was carrying a violin.

00:09:16.790 --> 00:09:21.950 align:middle line:84%
>> She was beautiful, and
fierce, and tough, and direct.

00:09:21.950 --> 00:09:24.800 align:middle line:84%
Anything that Sharon did,
I was pretty in awe of.

00:09:24.800 --> 00:09:27.380 align:middle line:90%


00:09:27.380 --> 00:09:30.510 align:middle line:84%
>> One evening, we're all
working there together.

00:09:30.510 --> 00:09:33.500 align:middle line:84%
David was, you know,
supervising, managing.

00:09:33.500 --> 00:09:38.660 align:middle line:84%
