know, at their love kind

00:09:53.300 --> 00:09:54.742 align:middle line:90%
of blossoming.

00:09:54.742 --> 00:09:56.450 align:middle line:84%
>> When they walked
into a room together,

00:09:56.450 --> 00:09:59.600 align:middle line:84%
