00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:08.477 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:10:08.477 --> 00:10:18.790 align:middle line:90%


00:10:18.790 --> 00:10:27.090 align:middle line:84%
>> I had felt, believed, was
devoted to the idea that art

00:10:27.090 --> 00:10:36.780 align:middle line:84%
