01:09:07.654 --> 01:09:09.490 align:middle line:90%
I see it taught in Puerto Rico.

01:09:09.490 --> 01:09:11.500 align:middle line:84%
I see it thought
in South America,

01:09:11.500 --> 01:09:15.120 align:middle line:90%
in Europe, in Asia, and India.

01:09:15.120 --> 01:09:16.229 align:middle line:90%
It's everywhere.

01:09:16.229 --> 01:09:19.790 align:middle line:90%


01:09:19.790 --> 01:09:23.080 align:middle line:84%
>> The teacher trainings
that we have draw an average

01:09:23.080 --> 01:09:27.930 align:middle line:84%
of students or teacher trainees
