01:09:27.930 --> 01:09:31.120 align:middle line:84%
who are bringing these teachings
back to where they came from.

01:09:31.120 --> 01:09:34.319 align:middle line:90%


01:09:34.319 --> 01:09:38.229 align:middle line:84%
>> Sharon and David have
inspired countless people.

01:09:38.229 --> 01:09:41.680 align:middle line:84%
They've been all over
the world teaching people

01:09:41.680 --> 01:09:45.330 align:middle line:84%
how to live a decent
life and how to be whole.

01:09:45.330 --> 01:09:47.800 align:middle line:84%
And I just think
they've changed so much

01:09:47.800 --> 01:09:50.660 align:middle line:84%
for so long, that I
take my hat off to them.

01:09:50.660 --> 01:09:54.580 align:middle line:90%


01:09:54.580 --> 01:09:57.510 align:middle line:84%
>> They've inspired so
many others to inspire.

01:09:57.510 --> 01:10:00.520 align:middle line:84%
You have Jivamukti teachers
all over the globe.

01:10:00.520 --> 01:10:04.740 align:middle line:84%
And to know that you're kind
of all working for this greater

01:10:04.740 --> 01:10:06.300 align:middle line:90%
good is hugely inspiring.

01:10:06.300 --> 01:10:08.820 align:middle line:84%
>> There are a lot of us now
out in the world who are doing

01:10:08.820 --> 01:10:10.110 align:middle line:90%
really good things.

01:10:10.110 --> 01:10:14.840 align:middle line:84%
We're taking yoga and we're
creating engaged spirituality.

01:10:14.840 --> 01:10:18.220 align:middle line:84%
David and Sharon, they're
the gurus behind that.

01:10:18.220 --> 01:10:23.790 align:middle line:84%
They're the impetus for a lot
of us to get up off the mat

01:10:23.790 --> 01:10:25.800 align:middle line:90%
and go out into the world.

01:10:25.800 --> 01:10:28.830 align:middle line:84%
>> What I love about them
is they stay in their truth.

01:10:28.830 --> 01:10:30.280 align:middle line:90%
They dare to care.

01:10:30.280 --> 01:10:32.820 align:middle line:84%
The work that they
do is unfaltering

01:10:32.820 --> 01:10:35.790 align:middle line:84%
and it inspires people to
be better than they ever

01:10:35.790 --> 01:10:38.688 align:middle line:90%
thought they could possibly be.

01:10:38.688 --> 01:10:42.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Jivamukti yoga has, just by
their focus and commitment--

01:10:42.600 --> 01:10:46.710 align:middle line:84%
it has just become worldwide
phenomenon, awakening,

01:10:46.710 --> 01:10:52.950 align:middle line:84%
ancient teachings, integrating
them, making them accessible.

01:10:52.950 --> 01:10:55.830 align:middle line:90%
And it's contagious, thank God.

01:10:55.830 --> 01:11:00.005 align:middle line:84%
>> We're working on growing
a community, growing a tribe,

01:11:00.005 --> 01:11:00.893 align:middle line:90%
you could say.

01:11:00.893 --> 01:11:01.900 align:middle line:90%
>> A global community.

01:11:01.900 --> 01:11:02.700 align:middle line:90%
>> A global tribe.

01:11:02.700 --> 01:11:05.100 align:middle line:84%
And a tribe just
means people feels

01:11:05.100 --> 01:11:09.930 align:middle line:84%
they have a common shared
experience that grows

01:11:09.930 --> 01:11:12.060 align:middle line:90%
in a natural, organic way.

01:11:12.060 --> 01:11:15.150 align:middle line:84%
>> I feel very blessed
and fortunate to be part

01:11:15.150 --> 01:11:20.760 align:middle line:84%
of something wonderful,
Jivamukti Yoga.

01:11:20.760 --> 01:11:23.130 align:middle line:84%
>> As I sat pondering a
worthwhile conclusion to this

01:11:23.130 --> 01:11:27.210 align:middle line:84%
film, I realized one
profound concept--

01:11:27.210 --> 01:11:29.380 align:middle line:90%
nobody has the answers.

01:11:29.380 --> 01:11:32.340 align:middle line:84%
As ironic or vague
as this may sound,

01:11:32.340 --> 01:11:34.860 align:middle line:84%
the answer was with
me all the time.

01:11:34.860 --> 01:11:38.420 align:middle line:84%
We spend our lives ruminating
on past and future events,

01:11:38.420 --> 01:11:41.370 align:middle line:84%
giving little, if any
attention to the present.

01:11:41.370 --> 01:11:44.820 align:middle line:84%
Playing victim to circumstance
seems easier than accepting

01:11:44.820 --> 01:11:47.190 align:middle line:84%
the fact that suffering is
the hand that pulls us out

01:11:47.190 --> 01:11:52.360 align:middle line:84%
of stagnation, and is possibly
best summed up by Rumi--

01:11:52.360 --> 01:11:55.450 align:middle line:84%
"This being human
is a guest house.

01:11:55.450 --> 01:12:00.820 align:middle line:84%
Every morning, a new arrival, a
joy, a depression, a meanness.

01:12:00.820 --> 01:12:04.840 align:middle line:84%
Some momentary awareness comes
as an unexpected visitor.

01:12:04.840 --> 01:12:07.450 align:middle line:90%
Welcome and entertain them all.

01:12:07.450 --> 01:12:09.610 align:middle line:84%
Be grateful for
whatever comes your way,

01:12:09.610 --> 01:12:11.380 align:middle line:84%
because each and
every moment has been

01:12:11.380 --> 01:12:15.440 align:middle line:90%
sent as a guide from beyond."

01:12:15.440 --> 01:12:19.490 align:middle line:84%
>> As science or the rational
mind digs deeper and deeper

01:12:19.490 --> 01:12:23.600 align:middle line:84%
into reality, past the
superficial aspects,

01:12:23.600 --> 01:12:27.950 align:middle line:84%
we find out not only do we know
less than we thought we do,

01:12:27.950 --> 01:12:30.920 align:middle line:84%
we also are discovering
that what we thought was one

01:12:30.920 --> 01:12:34.760 align:middle line:84%
universe is a system
of multiverse.

01:12:34.760 --> 01:12:36.590 align:middle line:90%
And we actually have a choice.

01:12:36.590 --> 01:12:38.600 align:middle line:84%
If you want to live in
a universe with no god,

01:12:38.600 --> 01:12:40.910 align:middle line:84%
you can choose to
do that because it's

01:12:40.910 --> 01:12:45.740 align:middle line:84%
the belief in our mind that
creates it or destroys it.

01:12:45.740 --> 01:12:49.520 align:middle line:84%
When I ask myself, is there
a god, is there not a god,

01:12:49.520 --> 01:12:51.680 align:middle line:90%
it really doesn't matter to me.

01:12:51.680 --> 01:12:57.170 align:middle line:84%
If I choose to believe there
is no god and I'm wrong,

01:12:57.170 --> 01:12:59.870 align:middle line:90%
I'm in trouble.

01:12:59.870 --> 01:13:06.290 align:middle line:84%
If I choose to believe there's
a god and I'm wrong, no problem.

01:13:06.290 --> 01:13:08.060 align:middle line:90%
I'm just dead.

01:13:08.060 --> 01:13:11.750 align:middle line:84%
That choice, it removes
any doubt from me.

01:13:11.750 --> 01:13:14.840 align:middle line:84%
Really, you can choose
to believe or disbelieve

01:13:14.840 --> 01:13:17.990 align:middle line:84%
and it's totally
irrelevant, except to you.

01:13:17.990 --> 01:13:22.610 align:middle line:84%
And in the end, there's
nothing, absolutely nothing,

01:13:22.610 --> 01:13:25.890 align:middle line:84%
and everything to
gain by believing.

01:13:25.890 --> 01:13:28.580 align:middle line:84%
>> When you see a film, and you
know it's just a play of light

01:13:28.580 --> 01:13:29.850 align:middle line:90%
on a surface.

01:13:29.850 --> 01:13:32.450 align:middle line:84%
So in a way, you know that
that vast, absolute thing

01:13:32.450 --> 01:13:35.430 align:middle line:84%
is like a surface on which
there is this play of light,

01:13:35.430 --> 01:13:37.880 align:middle line:84%
but it's not the surface
without the play of light.

01:13:37.880 --> 01:13:39.680 align:middle line:84%
It's a surface with
the play of light.

01:13:39.680 --> 01:13:42.800 align:middle line:10%
And why that's so
important is then

01:13:42.800 --> 01:13:45.500 align:middle line:10%
you feel great
love and compassion

01:13:45.500 --> 01:13:49.460 align:middle line:10%
for those other sensitive
beings in the unreally real who

01:13:49.460 --> 01:13:52.000 align:middle line:10%
don't know that it's
only unreally real.

01:13:52.000 --> 01:13:55.700 align:middle line:84%
They think that their individual
selves, separate from others,

01:13:55.700 --> 01:13:58.340 align:middle line:84%
is really real, and
then they suffer.

01:13:58.340 --> 01:14:01.850 align:middle line:84%
So Jivamukti, being
living and liberated,

01:14:01.850 --> 01:14:05.280 align:middle line:84%
means that you're
back with the living.

01:14:05.280 --> 01:14:07.850 align:middle line:84%
And you are liberated in
that you can take anything,

01:14:07.850 --> 01:14:11.020 align:middle line:84%
because you know that
it's only unreally real.

01:14:11.020 --> 01:14:14.780 align:middle line:84%
But you won't take
the other people

01:14:14.780 --> 01:14:19.330 align:middle line:84%
who think it's really real
continuing to really suffer.

01:14:19.330 --> 01:14:23.570 align:middle line:84%
That is to say, your drive
for absolute knowledge,

01:14:23.570 --> 01:14:25.700 align:middle line:84%
and absolute freedom,
absolute bliss

01:14:25.700 --> 01:14:27.590 align:middle line:84%
becomes love and
compassion for those

01:14:27.590 --> 01:14:29.392 align:middle line:90%
who do not have that condition.

01:14:29.392 --> 01:14:31.850 align:middle line:84%
>> These are things that we
just take for granted, I think,

01:14:31.850 --> 01:14:32.650 align:middle line:90%
in yoga.

01:14:32.650 --> 01:14:34.940 align:middle line:84%
Like, we're all in the
search for what is real

01:14:34.940 --> 01:14:37.400 align:middle line:90%
as if it was somewhere else.

01:14:37.400 --> 01:14:39.110 align:middle line:90%
>> I prefer the unreal.

01:14:39.110 --> 01:14:43.669 align:middle line:84%
And like Castaneda said,
there's the tonal universe,

01:14:43.669 --> 01:14:45.210 align:middle line:84%
and that's the one
we think we're in,

01:14:45.210 --> 01:14:47.480 align:middle line:84%
and we're all conducting
ourselves correctly.

01:14:47.480 --> 01:14:50.390 align:middle line:84%
And then there's the nagual,
and that's the unknown.

01:14:50.390 --> 01:14:54.290 align:middle line:84%
>> What is real is the light
of the self that exists in all

01:14:54.290 --> 01:14:56.750 align:middle line:90%
of us, and that we have to feel.

01:14:56.750 --> 01:14:59.160 align:middle line:84%
>> I think everything
else is an illusion.

01:14:59.160 --> 01:15:00.980 align:middle line:90%
It's like a big hallucination.

01:15:00.980 --> 01:15:04.820 align:middle line:84%
It is something that our
ego mind came up with.

01:15:04.820 --> 01:15:07.160 align:middle line:84%
>> What's real is that
you're not the body.

01:15:07.160 --> 01:15:09.050 align:middle line:84%
What's real is that
you're an eternal soul.

01:15:09.050 --> 01:15:11.296 align:middle line:84%
This body comes
and this body goes.

01:15:11.296 --> 01:15:13.170 align:middle line:84%
The only thing that
remains is consciousness.

01:15:13.170 --> 01:15:15.544 align:middle line:84%
You remember when you were
living in the body of a child.

01:15:15.544 --> 01:15:16.630 align:middle line:90%
Where's that body now?

01:15:16.630 --> 01:15:17.630 align:middle line:90%
It's gone.

01:15:17.630 --> 01:15:20.030 align:middle line:90%
Now you're in an adult body.

01:15:20.030 --> 01:15:22.370 align:middle line:84%
A few years, you'll
leave this body,

01:15:22.370 --> 01:15:25.250 align:middle line:84%
and then consciousness
will go to some other body.

01:15:25.250 --> 01:15:26.210 align:middle line:90%
That's real.

01:15:26.210 --> 01:15:29.780 align:middle line:84%
Now the trick is to access
that, to get to that.

01:15:29.780 --> 01:15:31.324 align:middle line:90%
That's why you practice yoga.

01:15:31.324 --> 01:15:32.990 align:middle line:84%
>> The nature of
things is impermanence.

01:15:32.990 --> 01:15:34.880 align:middle line:84%
If there is no separate
self, then that

01:15:34.880 --> 01:15:38.690 align:middle line:84%
means there's no separation
between even you and a god.

01:15:38.690 --> 01:15:40.670 align:middle line:90%
That goes beyond oneness.

01:15:40.670 --> 01:15:42.350 align:middle line:90%
It's like zeroness.

01:15:42.350 --> 01:15:44.810 align:middle line:84%
Responsibility
can't fall any less

01:15:44.810 --> 01:15:50.360 align:middle line:84%
than what you do has absolutely
an impression on the lives

01:15:50.360 --> 01:15:54.410 align:middle line:84%
and the well-being of others
around you and vice versa.

01:15:54.410 --> 01:15:56.900 align:middle line:84%
>> Things are real that
increase your "bhav,"

01:15:56.900 --> 01:15:59.750 align:middle line:84%
increase your connection
to the divine,

01:15:59.750 --> 01:16:03.200 align:middle line:84%
take you away from selfish,
materialistic way of living.

01:16:03.200 --> 01:16:05.750 align:middle line:90%
>> This will not last forever.

01:16:05.750 --> 01:16:08.750 align:middle line:84%
That's what's real--
that this is temporary.

01:16:08.750 --> 01:16:10.590 align:middle line:90%
>> You and I are real.

01:16:10.590 --> 01:16:13.310 align:middle line:84%
The trees, everything is
breathing, everything is real.

01:16:13.310 --> 01:16:17.540 align:middle line:84%
Everything is just that
emanation of truth and glory

01:16:17.540 --> 01:16:19.400 align:middle line:90%
and compassion.

01:16:19.400 --> 01:16:20.334 align:middle line:90%
It's all real.

01:16:20.334 --> 01:16:22.250 align:middle line:84%
>> But in the process
of everything being one,

01:16:22.250 --> 01:16:24.515 align:middle line:84%
it doesn't mean that
everything goes away.

01:16:24.515 --> 01:16:28.470 align:middle line:84%
It means the diversity and the
beautiful expansion of Narayan

01:16:28.470 --> 01:16:30.350 align:middle line:90%
himself remains.

01:16:30.350 --> 01:16:33.710 align:middle line:84%
But within that, there
is a single essence

01:16:33.710 --> 01:16:36.050 align:middle line:90%
that permeates everything.

01:16:36.050 --> 01:16:40.520 align:middle line:84%
To taste that essence that
exists everywhere and is also

01:16:40.520 --> 01:16:46.210 align:middle line:84%
within every heart is what
the Bhakti Yoga experience

01:16:46.210 --> 01:16:47.180 align:middle line:90%
is about.

01:16:47.180 --> 01:16:49.090 align:middle line:84%
>> We get to use these
bodies for a while.

01:16:49.090 --> 01:16:52.000 align:middle line:84%
We get to enjoy the
earth for a while.

01:16:52.000 --> 01:16:54.650 align:middle line:90%
And it will all go back to dust.

01:16:54.650 --> 01:16:56.938 align:middle line:84%
So what are you
going to do today?

